```plantuml
@startuml apigee_consumer-data-standards-au

!define RECTANGLE class

rectangle "Apigee API Management Platform" as Apigee {
    [CDS Banking API Proxies] as BankingAPI
    [OIDC Proxy] as OIDC
    [ConsentMgmtWithKVM Proxy] as ConsentMgmt
    [Dynamic Client Registration] as ClientReg
    [Shared Flows] as SharedFlows
    [Admin APIs] as AdminAPI
}

cloud "External Systems" {
    [External OIDC Provider] as ExtOIDC
    [CDR Register] as CDRRegister
}

rectangle "Google Cloud Platform" {
    [App Engine] as AppEngine
    [Metrics Service] as MetricsService
}

[Mock OIDC Provider] as MockOIDC
[Client Applications] as ClientApps

ClientApps --> Apigee : API Requests
Apigee --> MockOIDC : Authentication (Dev/Test)
Apigee --> ExtOIDC : Authentication (Production)
Apigee --> CDRRegister : Register Interaction
BankingAPI --> SharedFlows : Use
OIDC --> SharedFlows : Use
ConsentMgmt --> SharedFlows : Use
ClientReg --> SharedFlows : Use
AdminAPI --> SharedFlows : Use
Apigee --> AppEngine : Deploy
AppEngine --> MetricsService : Host
MetricsService --> Apigee : Collect Analytics

@enduml
```